अजवीथि|ajaviithi
--on the back of the शिशुमार (s.v.) {{F}}1:  भा. V. २३. 5.{{/F}} the southern course. Here are three kinds of sunrise, one in मूल and the other two in two आषाढस्; on its south was पितृयान: consists of three constellations--मूल and आषा- ढस्--पूर्व and उत्तर। {{F}}2:  Br. II. २१. ७६ & १५९; III. 3. ५१; M. १२४. ५३-8; वा. 1. ९३; ६६. ५१; Vi. II. 8. ८५.{{/F}} [page१-031+ २८]

