--a special rite in the यज्ञस् after the cele- brated sage Atri. वा. ७०. ७३.

अथर्वन्|atharvan
 (I)--married शान्ति, a daughter of Kardama. It was he who spread यज्ञ in the world. {{F}}1:  भा. III. २४. २४.{{/F}} His son was दध्यञ्च who had a horse's head. {{F}}2:  Ib. IV. 1. ४२.{{/F}} [page१-043+ २९]

