 (I)--a son of ब्रह्मा, born of his back. {{F}}1:  भा. III. १२. २५.{{/F}} Had for his wife म्र्षा. {{F}}2:  Ib. IV. 8. 2.{{/F}} Three chief characteristics--pride, luxury and intoxication. {{F}}3:  Ib. I. १७. २४.{{/F}} His son was Dambha and daughter माया, both of whom were adopted later on by the [page१-046+ ३३] childless निरृति. {{F}}4:  Ib. IV. 8. 2.{{/F}} Five branches of: विधर्म, परधर्म, आभास, उपमा, and छल। {{F}}5:  Ib. VII. १५. १२-14.{{/F}}

