--a forest sacred to अम्बिका on the banks of the सरस्वती. Here was a festival in honour of शिव and देवी. To this, Nanda and others went. When he was there, [page१-091+ २५] Nanda was seized by a reptile, and was released by कृष्ण. {{F}}1:  भा. X. ३४. 1-१८.{{/F}} Before her marriage रुक्मिणी went to worship in this shrine. {{F}}2:  Ib. X. ५३. ३९.{{/F}}

