ईश्वर|iishvara
--also महेश्वर and शङ्कर; a Rudra: place of residence is शिवपुर in front of Brahmaloka; Lord of Trinity; {{F}}1:  Br. III. 3. ७१; IV. ३९. १२०; M. १७१. ३९.{{/F}} the अधिदेवता for the planet सूर्य; {{F}}2:  M. ९३. १३.{{/F}} the २६थ् तत्व on one view; {{F}}3:  M. 3. २८.{{/F}} being a small atom is god of love for people; in him are ten characteristics--knowledge, वैराग्य, ऐश्वर्य, तपस्, सत्य, patience, courage, quality of being seen, kinship to self and dominion; is माया or illusory; {{F}}4:  वा. १०१. २१५, २१९; Br. IV. 2. २१७.{{/F}} the Lord of all world. {{F}}5:  वा. 4. ३६ and ४२.{{/F}} [page१-207+ १२]

