चैत्ररथी|chaitrarathii
 (also बिन्दुमती)--the daughter of शश- bindu and wife of मान्धात; had १०,000 younger brothers; righteous, fair and chaste; mother of three sons Purukutsu, अम्बरिष and Mucukunda. Br. III. ६३. ७०; वा. ८८. ७०-2. [page१-613+ ३६]

