दुर्योधन|duryodhana
--the eldest of the hundred sons of धृत- राष्ट्र and गान्धारि; {{F}}1:  भा. IX. २२. २६; X. ६४. [4]; M. ५०. ४८; वा. ९९. २४३; Vi. IV. २०. ३९.{{/F}} सुभद्रा was intended by राम to be given in marriage to him; {{F}}2:  भा. X. ८६. 3.{{/F}} was met by कृतवर्मन् and taken leave of; {{F}}3:  Ib. X. ५२. (५६. V. १२).{{/F}} went from Balabhadra and learnt गदा from बलराम at मिथिला; {{F}}4:  Ib. X. ५७. २६; Br. III. ७१. ८४; वा. ९६. ८३.{{/F}} mistook the colour of the flooring of the पाण्डव's सभा (built by Maya) for a sheet of water and had a nasty fall at which भीम and the ladies laughed. This enraged Duryodhana who was conciliated by युधिष्ठिर who sent clothes to him through कृष्ण. He did not accept them, but went home downcast; {{F}}5:  भा. X. ५८. २७; ७५. ३४-39.{{/F}} kept under influence Vinda and Anuvinda of Avanti; {{F}}6:  Ib. X. ५८. ३०.{{/F}} banished the पाण्डवस् and द्रौपदी to the forest for defeat in the game of dice; {{F}}7:  Ib. X. ६४. [4].{{/F}} resented साम्ब's action in taking away his daughter लक्ष्मणा in स्वयम्वर and wanted to punish him; heard of राम's arrival and extended welcome to him; afraid of राम's prowess agreed to the marriage of his daughter to साम्ब and gave a rich dowry; {{F}}8:  Ib. X. ६८. (whole); Vi. V. ३५. 4-5, ११.{{/F}} did not feel happy over the success of the राजसूय, where he was in charge of the treasury; {{F}}9:  भा. X. ७४. ५३; ७५. 2 and 4.{{/F}} failed to hit the fish mark in लक्ष्मणा's स्वयम्वर; {{F}}१०:  Ib. X. ८३. २३.{{/F}} Jealous of कृष्ण and द्रौपदी, his mind set on the latter; {{F}}११:  Ib. X. ७५. ३१-32.{{/F}} ordered Vidura's banishment for offering good counsel, and insulted him as the son of a दासि; {{F}}१२:  Ib. I. 7. १४; III. 1. १४-15.{{/F}} met the पाण्डवस् in war at कुरुक्षेत्र; arranged in व्यूह at Syamanta- [page२-105+ ३९] पञ्चक; fought with भीमसेन who killed him with his गद; lay in the battlefield with his thigh fractured, along with eleven अक्षौहिणिस्. {{F}}१३:  Ib. X. ७८ (१६ (V) १५, १८-19), ३९; ७९. २३; ८० [1]; III. 3. १३; M. १०३. 3-5.{{/F}} Built a house of lac to get the पाण्डवस् consumed by flames. {{F}}१४:  Vi. IV. १३. ७०.{{/F}}

