t ancient of the पुराणस्; {{F}}१३:  Ib. ५८. 4, ५०; ६९. १८.{{/F}} the पुराण version of वराह Avata1ra attributed to ब्रह्मा; {{F}}१४:  Ib. २४७. 1, 5.{{/F}} the पुराण in general partakes the character of the epoch in which it is composed; {{F}}१५:  Ib. २९०. १५.{{/F}} recital of, during स्राद्ध. {{F}}१६:  Ib. १७. ३७.{{/F}}

