प्रकृतिस्|prakRtis
 (I)--seven kinds, which support the monarch. भा. VI. १४. १७-18.

प्रकृतिस्|prakRtis
 (II)--usually eight, the eight places of gods, from ब्रह्मा to पिशाच, eight-fold ऐश्वर्य, the eight रूपस्, etc. {{F}}1:  Br. IV. 3. २७ to ७३.{{/F}} regarded as truth and their opposite as false. {{F}}2:  Ib. IV. 3. ८५.{{/F}} [page२-401+ ३१]

प्रकृतिस्|prakRtis
