मन्मथ|manmatha
--(काम); God of Love; {{F}}1:  M. ११८. १३.{{/F}} on the third Parva of the Geyacakra; {{F}}2:  Br. IV. १९. ६७.{{/F}} recreated by ललिता, who said he was her son; went to शिव's abode accompanied by his friend Vasanta. {{F}}3:  Ib. IV. ३०. ४६.{{/F}} Got burnt by शिव and in effecting his revival मायवती (रती) deluded शम्बर by her charms; she brought up Pradyumna who was a part of the Love God. {{F}}4:  VI. V. २७. २८-30.{{/F}} [page२-633+ २९]

