सौभाग्यव्रतम्|saubhaagyavratam
--in honour of भवानी. M. १०१. १६.

सौभाग्यशयनम्|saubhaagyashayanam
--in honour of उमा; to be begun on Vasanta शुक्ल triti1ya1 and continued for a year every त्रितीया when सती married शिव; after purificatory baths, offer prayers to उमा and also to शिव in the midst of the eight सौभाग्यस् by flowers, incense, etc.; at the end a gift of a bed is prescribed; the performer gets desired things and ultimately reaches heaven; he who does it for १२ years, or 7 or 8 lives a happy long life. Madana, Sata- dhanva, कार्तवीर्य, वरुण and Nandi have done this. M. ६०. 1. ४६. [page३-705+ २५]

