--a division of श्रिपुरम्. Br. IV. ३२. २५.

हरिण|hariNa
--see Haraya. Br. III. 7. १७९; २२. ४५.

हरिणाकूडनम्|hariNaakuuDanam
--Boyish sport, in which boys are coupled with one another and go leaping away; the vanguard brings back the victor to the starting ground; Govinda was matched with श्रीदामन् and राम with Pralamba in the disguise of a Gopa. Vi. V. 9. १२-14. [page३-750+ २४]

